    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You unleash a virulent disease on a creature that you can see within range. The target must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, it takes 14d6 necrotic damage, or half as much damage on a successful save. The damage cant reduce the targets Hit Points below 1. If the target fails the saving throw, its hit point maximum is reduced for 1 Hour by an amount equal to the necrotic damage it took. Any effect that removes a disease allows a creatures hit point maximum to return to normal before that time passes.</p>",
